# Urja AI — Full Stack Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete full-stack campus energy optimization system split into two directories: `backend/` (FastAPI) and `frontend/` (React + Vite + Tailwind CSS).

---

## Backend (`d:/urja-ai/UrjaAI/backend/`)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `app/main.py` | FastAPI app, CORS middleware, all routers mounted |
| `app/schemas/predict.py` | Pydantic schemas for all 4 API endpoints |
| `app/services/ml.py` | **Partner integration point** — 2 stubbed functions with `# TODO: ML` |
| `app/services/data.py` | CSV data loader with synthetic fallback |
| `app/routers/predict.py` | `POST /predict` |
| `app/routers/recommendations.py` | `POST /recommendations` — rule-based, no ML |
| `app/routers/explain.py` | `POST /explain` |
| `app/routers/whatif.py` | `POST /whatif` |
| `data/README.md` | CSV format spec for real sensor data |
| `requirements.txt` | All dependencies (already installed) |

**To run backend:**
```bash
cd d:/urja-ai/UrjaAI/backend
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
# Open http://localhost:8000/docs
```

---

## Frontend (`d:/urja-ai/UrjaAI/frontend/`)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `src/services/api.js` | Axios wrapper — auto falls back to mock data |
| `src/services/mockData.js` | Static mock responses for all 4 endpoints |
| `src/hooks/useDashboard.js` | Central state hook with debounced what-if |
| `src/components/Header.jsx` | Building selector + datetime |
| `src/components/MetricsCards.jsx` | 3 glassmorphism stat cards |
| `src/components/ForecastChart.jsx` | Recharts line + confidence band + what-if overlay |
| `src/components/RecommendationsPanel.jsx` | Cards with "Why?" accordions |
| `src/components/ExplainabilitySection.jsx` | SHAP bar chart + explanation text |
| `src/components/WhatIfControls.jsx` | Temperature + occupancy sliders (debounced) |
| `src/pages/Dashboard.jsx` | Responsive 2-column grid page |

**To run frontend:**
```bash
cd d:/urja-ai/UrjaAI/frontend
npm run dev
# Open http://localhost:5173
```

